	(text "W25Q16JVUXIQ Datasheet p6 -> Use a 100nF and 1uF capacitor\nRPI Pico Schematic -> Use a 100nF and 2uF decoupling capacitors. A pull up resistor is not fitted\nHardware design with rp2040 p9 -> Use a 100nF decoupling capacitor. Pull up resistor is not fitted, the flash can work without it. \nI will only place the 100nF capacitor, since the devboard can work according to Hardware design guide. I will not place a pull up resitor\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 33.655 137.16 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2 2)
			)
			(justify left bottom)
		)
		(uuid "6d3a2c25-ef00-463f-a8f9-097d65411ee9")
	)
